<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8" standalone="no"?><?Xpress productLine="ncc-clause" ?><clause xmlns:qxa="true" xmlns:xt="urn:xpressauthor:trackchanges" id="_822e6329-c7e6-46fe-b5e1-61472ff979ed" outputclass="ncc-clause"><sptc>B5V1</sptc><title id="_b05b57a2-2012-4951-9e28-f486ecd25179">Determination of individual and zone hazard ratings</title><archive-num>New for 2022</archive-num><subclause id="_5b092f4e-f567-482a-8c68-58947acfe574" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_263311a1-8f24-445c-a43e-3ebab8e721f5">SubClause</title><num>1</num><p>Compliance with <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1395_4.0.0.xml#_f7304862-3529-49d7-9f62-352bcbcb6294" id="_04f12507-3c25-454d-a706-79cd083b257e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Performance Requirement</xref> <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1706_1.5.0.xml#_c3b8a47f-fb69-4db2-8d70-1722ad82032d" id="_e6ca2309-b34d-4549-9d21-2e5cf114f120" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">B5P1</xref> for <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1349_3.0.0.xml#_9f04cdcd-91b5-41a3-81b7-1243261eb779" id="_b1a6d60b-36fc-425c-8086-c36f062b230e" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">individual protection</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1527_28.0.0.xml#_fdc3535a-4b9d-49c2-add5-cb0a1b466b51" id="_3cef7397-60fb-4b1d-ba83-14781c7c5e2c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">zone protection</xref> is verified by compliance with B5V1.</p></subclause><subclause id="_4dbb5132-8c7e-4cf1-a5ac-4c097369a2d2" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_96a89cc4-5d29-44f9-a240-b2a5d5ff3fc4">SubClause</title><num>2</num><p>A hazard exists wherever it is possible for water or <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1228_0.6.0.xml#_a7483c3c-cd8a-4c37-8f2b-8e4fba0e0989" id="_3a8619bb-d36c-4a25-b0de-381b0818b346" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">contaminants</xref> to enter  service or supply via any potential or actual <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1233_1.0.0.xml#_b3f409ec-8f72-48d9-8a64-0dc9d5fb5d67" id="_1a65f876-08a9-40e2-b8e3-a51f7eea95de" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">cross-connection</xref> between itself and any other separate water service on the same <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1463_0.4.0.xml#_fb3536f6-7ee5-4a29-a4da-402a8e1168dc" id="_c6487f85-4a49-414c-9756-3ad002b4f06f" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">site</xref>.</p></subclause><subclause id="_baab4a7c-5b8a-4ded-bad4-47fa83c11e0a" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_34b91295-c541-4775-9b86-f4f306735f1c">SubClause</title><num>3</num><p>Each hazard must be—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_13ffbe94-2038-4028-8892-c50609982cec">assigned a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1332_3.6.0.xml#_e221b82c-bc4b-43d2-ab64-522dd5dd1885" id="_bd817dd5-434d-4d46-8500-ceff70abb79a" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Hazard Rating</xref> in accordance with (4); and </li><li id="_47814bf8-7bc4-427e-8d62-ecee5ffd76d1">isolated from the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1250_0.7.0.xml#_762d6a54-e28c-400b-b9c5-5fceac019a05" id="_d51a5a8e-358e-43e9-bab8-90bdcb9911ba" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">drinking water</xref> service by an appropriate <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1204_1.0.0.xml#_0fd1c6f9-50b2-4e0c-bda6-25c2bf33379f" id="_a90433ef-71ee-4a8f-b270-b29de27cddc7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">backflow prevention device</xref> which is selected and installed for the appropriate <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1332_3.6.0.xml#_e221b82c-bc4b-43d2-ab64-522dd5dd1885" id="_ae4d552a-3bb3-4b48-bcb4-2ef105806577" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Hazard Rating</xref> in accordance with AS/NZS 3500.1.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_0f63540d-6ebf-4fdb-a09c-7ba29907354d" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_0d90db7b-6d26-4736-8467-7e00ef39deef">SubClause</title><num>4</num><p>To determine the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1332_3.6.0.xml#_e221b82c-bc4b-43d2-ab64-522dd5dd1885" id="_9e6aa195-33d4-4065-824b-b8325b16e663" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Hazard Rating</xref>—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_f9c69d00-8338-4ab5-8da8-3ed6a0a57c01">an assessment of the property or proposed installation must be undertaken using <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/5067_0.13.0.xml#_40cc5c4d-e8cc-4f33-b592-63c314b17050" id="_11b26452-1305-4a02-9a00-9f100f5d7666" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">Tables B5V1a</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/5068_0.14.0.xml#_e63ba582-7c8e-484b-a9f5-5e49afda27f2" id="_195b3f6b-59a6-44e8-b1cf-a13d13352644" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">B5V1b</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/5069_0.10.0.xml#_32f5436c-874d-4a52-888e-3d7b929598ae" id="_eb6b2620-cbd5-4045-bba9-05917dfd2827" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">B5V1c</xref>, <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/5071_0.13.0.xml#_de4736fa-c472-49ff-bdbf-42a685fe1a4d" id="_5c86af35-45df-4f02-97ab-1493667c19b0" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">B5V1d</xref> and <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/5074_0.10.0.xml#_bbe9b444-7edf-4265-a92c-3765fdabf2de" id="_93ca1ee6-7b0a-4d67-9ba8-16365ac62456" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="table-reference">B5V1e</xref>; and</li><li id="_b5b22ca9-e522-43c7-af4d-928db750e4e2">the scores allocated from each table are calculated; and </li><li id="_e27820e1-43a8-4b20-921f-6c4ef49b8906">the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1332_3.6.0.xml#_e221b82c-bc4b-43d2-ab64-522dd5dd1885" id="_1049003f-80db-40c2-933e-f21a8d352413" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Hazard Rating</xref> is determined by the sum of the scores in accordance with B5V1(5).</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_cdcd509a-f141-4fe5-8acf-9c64fd6216c0" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_c01569df-5ba4-41a6-8431-027dca7bdd51">SubClause</title><num>5</num><p>A total score of—</p><ol outputclass="alpha"><li id="_5209a76e-2445-4abd-9c77-a9f60d45d9a3">0 to 3 presents no Hazard; and</li><li id="_c5b6ab2b-5068-4879-a872-d60f97cc4495">4 to 7 presents a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1363_0.5.0.xml#_a0833472-40bb-4aef-be33-83a99f580c7c" id="_d0af34cf-bcfb-4c08-9492-a217bcb804a1" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Low Hazard</xref>; and</li><li id="_4ea32b6d-fcdb-4799-b2a3-348684bd4f54">8 to 10 presents a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1370_0.4.0.xml#_9edf8e98-0620-4b05-87e0-2ad738cb12b3" id="_a9654039-477e-4145-b414-533698ebef69" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Medium Hazard</xref>; and</li><li id="_f5cf3896-ed1f-4294-8ded-46896ac61050">11 or greater presents a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1338_0.4.0.xml#_ef1e79a4-57f6-4a86-8d5f-ba231ba4e684" id="_e7553ced-3b57-42b3-b617-719b1ec5256c" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">High Hazard</xref>.</li></ol></subclause><subclause id="_f10ea76b-1025-487b-936d-6d0975080b0d" outputclass="subclause"><title id="_474e04c2-605b-44bd-8ba6-6245a024158e">SubClause</title><num>6</num><p>Notwithstanding the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1332_3.6.0.xml#_e221b82c-bc4b-43d2-ab64-522dd5dd1885" id="_f1074907-3d85-47a1-a559-8a0f0f7b9c71" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Hazard Rating</xref> determined in (4), where access to the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1463_0.4.0.xml#_fb3536f6-7ee5-4a29-a4da-402a8e1168dc" id="_41a67d12-9ab8-4c68-84f6-82bd51c725cb" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">site</xref> is restricted in a way that could limit or prevent future testing or maintenance of a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1204_1.0.0.xml#_0fd1c6f9-50b2-4e0c-bda6-25c2bf33379f" id="_c23b4c3d-c803-4056-b570-11297e4c46d6" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">backflow prevention device</xref>, the <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1463_0.4.0.xml#_fb3536f6-7ee5-4a29-a4da-402a8e1168dc" id="_a1dd33cc-f36f-4339-9658-dfee3de183a2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">site</xref> must be protected with a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1227_1.0.0.xml#_f80df168-6569-4558-86ed-6d4b94202ea0" id="_c8215985-b6ef-42f4-a6de-fc155dc137d7" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">containment</xref> device suitable for a <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1338_0.4.0.xml#_ef1e79a4-57f6-4a86-8d5f-ba231ba4e684" id="_6e221d81-5387-4fe5-a67e-48c636b2f6f6" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">High Hazard</xref>.</p></subclause><callout id="_e34f4f3c-0ff9-4e46-b0ff-9d6f62780311"><callout-type ncc-info-type="info"/><ul outputclass="numbered"><li>The intent of this <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1506_27.0.0.xml#_a953dcf6-ebab-404f-a3f1-6d85f87ab898" id="_c40d4173-1b00-47f4-b880-71f3b13b0524" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Verification Method</xref> is to provide a consistent means of determining individual and zone <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1332_3.6.0.xml#_e221b82c-bc4b-43d2-ab64-522dd5dd1885" id="_f90e0a20-a80e-43f0-92db-9e96d4a81028" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Hazard Ratings</xref></li><li>This <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1506_27.0.0.xml#_a953dcf6-ebab-404f-a3f1-6d85f87ab898" id="_cc509de2-7330-4584-9abe-748237300de2" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Verification Method</xref> is not intended to enable the lowering of any <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/1332_3.6.0.xml#_e221b82c-bc4b-43d2-ab64-522dd5dd1885" id="_90950d44-d2eb-4bf3-8028-d6522654c355" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="abcb-glossentry">Hazard Ratings</xref> already prescribed in <xref format="dita" href="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/4242_0.16.0.xml#_815b95f4-12a3-405d-b360-2949ec359dcf" id="_7e6d3655-f0c6-423d-902c-4e62b9d2b2ff" referencetype="Text" scope="local" synctargettext="false" type="ncc-clause">B5D7</xref>.</li></ul></callout><table-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/5067_0.13.0.xml" graph="None" id="_40cc5c4d-e8cc-4f33-b592-63c314b17050"><num/><title id="_d3b4773b-1806-4e88-abd9-051c1d3c0007"/></table-reference><table-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/5068_0.14.0.xml" graph="None" id="_e63ba582-7c8e-484b-a9f5-5e49afda27f2"><num/><title id="_ead59f9c-7e7f-46b6-85e3-418ac56636b6"/></table-reference><table-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/5069_0.10.0.xml" graph="None" id="_32f5436c-874d-4a52-888e-3d7b929598ae"><num/><title id="_3ad05f9c-7ad5-41cd-9a16-edd26b8faff7"/></table-reference><table-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/5071_0.13.0.xml" graph="None" id="_de4736fa-c472-49ff-bdbf-42a685fe1a4d"><num/><title id="_3be7676e-0394-4aa2-a656-23d2e542ac05"/></table-reference><table-reference conref="/tmp/QppServer/Publishing/1c3f2f74-4ee1-4cdd-b1b4-53c91069d002/5074_0.10.0.xml" graph="None" id="_bbe9b444-7edf-4265-a92c-3765fdabf2de"><num/><title id="_ccf51689-5ae0-4973-8d33-ac777292482d"/></table-reference></clause>